          <ul class="drawer-h5">
            <li>触屏端如何使用cookie</li>
            <li>1、安装 npm install -g  nrm </li>
            <li>2、添加爱卡私有库源地址 nrm  add  xnpm --- http:\/\/registry.npm.op.xcar.com.cn:8081\/repository\/npm-group  切换爱卡镜像源</li>
            <li>3、安装npm install swiper;</li>
            <li>4、JS中引入 import Swiper from 'swiper';</li>
            <li>5、当前swiper版本为1.0.6</li>
            <li><span style="color:red;">  Tip:  </span>public文件夹存放公共样式</li>
            <li class="drawer-sili">代码实例</li>
            <li>
<pre style="overflow-x:auto;">
  <code>
/*js逻辑*/
mySwiper = new Swiper('dom', {
  loop:  true ,  //是否循环
  autoplay: 3000, //自动播放时间
  autoplayDisableOnInteraction: false, //点击后是否停止播放
  pagination: '.swiper-pagination-bullets',  //导航点点
  observer: true 
});    
  </code>
</pre>              
